title: Catherine Ringer sings Les Rita Mitsouko - July 2008
description:
This is the last Concert that Catherine Ringer sang the Songs she played
with her partner as "Les Rita Mitsouko".
This is a TV capture from Macintosh iTv, i just copied the file to my Win PC
and did not change the compression.

Languages spoken are french and german, but don't mind, it's not that much
talking. 

Thanks to ARTE for broadcasting and worship to me for sharing ;-)
